mation, and\nalert timeliness; we demonstrate that geodetic algorithms add significant\nvalue, including better cost savings performance, to EEW systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2019 22:26:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-28"}
