RN design\nparameters which can be jointly set for a desired signal distortion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2019 07:10:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 09:37:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-27"}
